    <item>
      <title>【笔记】Mac自动操作</title>
      <link>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/22/Mac%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</link>
      <guid>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/22/Mac%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Apr 2021 05:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac使用&lt;code&gt;自动操作.app&lt;/code&gt;创建&lt;code&gt;快速操作&lt;/code&gt;项目，并以&lt;code&gt;服务&lt;/code&gt;功能在系统菜单中出现&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>Mac使用<code>自动操作.app</code>创建<code>快速操作</code>项目，并以<code>服务</code>功能在系统菜单中出现</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="创建服务"><a href="#创建服务" class="headerlink" title="创建服务"></a>创建服务</h2><ul><li><code>快速操作.app</code>-&gt;<code>新建文稿</code>-&gt;<code>快速操作</code>-&gt;<code>选取</code></li></ul><p><img src="/images/20210422133918/01.png" alt="01.png"></p><ul><li>编辑工作流-&gt;保存工作流并为<code>服务</code>命名</li></ul><h2 id="编辑服务"><a href="#编辑服务" class="headerlink" title="编辑服务"></a>编辑服务</h2><ul><li><code>系统偏好设置</code>-&gt;<code>键盘</code>-&gt;<code>快捷键</code>-&gt;<code>服务</code>-&gt;找到保存的快速操作-&gt;右键-&gt;<code>在自动操作中打开</code></li></ul><p><img src="/images/20210422133918/02.png" alt="02.png"></p><ul><li>服务文件存放位置<code>~/Library/Services</code></li></ul><h2 id="完成"><a href="#完成" class="headerlink" title="完成"></a>完成</h2>]]></content:encoded>
      
      <comments>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/22/Mac%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/#disqus_thread</comments>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>【笔记】创建自己的第三方组件</title>
      <link>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/22/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/</link>
      <guid>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/22/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Apr 2021 05:09:15 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;使用微信官方脚手架&lt;code&gt;miniprogram-cli&lt;/code&gt;创建自己的微信小程序第三方组件&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>使用微信官方脚手架<code>miniprogram-cli</code>创建自己的微信小程序第三方组件</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="全局安装脚手架"><a href="#全局安装脚手架" class="headerlink" title="全局安装脚手架"></a>全局安装脚手架</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g @wechat-miniprogram/miniprogram-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="查看帮助"><a href="#查看帮助" class="headerlink" title="查看帮助"></a>查看帮助</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">miniprogram --<span class="built_in">help</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建一个项目"><a href="#创建一个项目" class="headerlink" title="创建一个项目"></a>创建一个项目</h2><ul><li>创建目录</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir demo &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">cd</span> demo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>初始化目录</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">miniprogram init --<span class="built_in">type</span> demo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>按需输入表单，什么也不输入就是默认值</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">which type of project want to use to initialize? &#x2F;&#x2F; 使用什么模版</span><br><span class="line">please input the package name? &#x2F;&#x2F; 包名</span><br><span class="line">please input the package version? &#x2F;&#x2F; 版本号</span><br><span class="line">please input the miniprogram dist folder？ &#x2F;&#x2F; 定义dist目录</span><br><span class="line">please input the git repository url? &#x2F;&#x2F; 定义仓库地址</span><br><span class="line">please input the author？ &#x2F;&#x2F; 定义作者</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装环境"><a href="#安装环境" class="headerlink" title="安装环境"></a>安装环境</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>环境安装完成会在项目根目录生成<code>node_modules</code>目录</li></ul><h2 id="导入项目"><a href="#导入项目" class="headerlink" title="导入项目"></a>导入项目</h2><ul><li><code>微信开发者工具</code>-&gt;<code>项目</code>-&gt;<code>导入项目</code></li></ul><h2 id="构建项目"><a href="#构建项目" class="headerlink" title="构建项目"></a>构建项目</h2><h3 id="安装构建工具（可选）"><a href="#安装构建工具（可选）" class="headerlink" title="安装构建工具（可选）"></a>安装构建工具（可选）</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g gulp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="开始构建"><a href="#开始构建" class="headerlink" title="开始构建"></a>开始构建</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gulp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="构建完成"><a href="#构建完成" class="headerlink" title="构建完成"></a>构建完成</h3><ul><li>构建完成后会在项目根目录生成<code>miniprogram_dist</code>目录</li></ul><h2 id="使用第三方组件"><a href="#使用第三方组件" class="headerlink" title="使用第三方组件"></a>使用第三方组件</h2><ul><li><p>将<code>miniprogram_dist</code>更名为第三方组件名</p></li><li><p>放置在小程序项目的<code>miniprogram-npm</code>，即可使用</p></li></ul><h2 id="发布第三方组件"><a href="#发布第三方组件" class="headerlink" title="发布第三方组件"></a>发布第三方组件</h2><ul><li>把创建完成的第三方组件发布到<a href="https://www.npmjs.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">npm社区官网</a></li></ul><p><a href="/2021/04/22/发布npm包/">传送门</a></p><h2 id="完成"><a href="#完成" class="headerlink" title="完成"></a>完成</h2><h2 id="参考文献"><a href="#参考文献" class="headerlink" title="参考文献"></a>参考文献</h2><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1kv411W73u" target="_blank" rel="noopener">哔哩哔哩——Python小清风</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      <comments>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/22/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/#disqus_thread</comments>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>【代码】动态展现标题栏案例</title>
      <link>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/21/%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%B1%95%E7%8E%B0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E6%A0%8F%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B/</link>
      <guid>https://feiju12138.github.io/2021/04/21/%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%B1%95%E7%8E%B0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E6%A0%8F%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Apr 2021 11:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;微信小程序动态展现标题栏案例&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>微信小程序动态展现标题栏案例</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="源代码"><a href="#源代码" class="headerlink" title="源代码"></a>源代码</h2><p><em>pages/components/nav/nav.wxml</em></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"nav"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">view</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">wx:for</span>=<span class="string">"&#123;&#123;key&#125;&#125;"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"&#123;&#123;a==index?'active':''&#125;&#125;"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">bindtap</span>=<span class="string">"click"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">data-a</span>=<span class="string">"&#123;&#123;index&#125;&#125;"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;&#123;item.title&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">view</span>&gt;</span>